          "plain_text": "Lunch time arrives suddenly. Maybe it’s the many coffees that we’ve consumed or maybe we’re having fun. Fred drops me at Jordan’s and comes in to admire her new hair do. I make a pretty fantastic eggy toast and spend some time just clearing out unread messages and whatnot. I continue digging around to try and find a motorcycle to rend in Malawi.",
