      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "It’s then Malawi fever as Jordan and I get really stuck into planning our trip. We find places along the bank of the lake that we could get to if it works out. That too flies by and suddenly it’s getting dark. We reflect on some lovely times over the last four years and then tackle what I find to be the hardest and most unenjoyable Wordle ever - ",
            "link": null
